{"tid":1363050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「請廣傳」幫烈士范先生既親屬發份聲明，有關范先生被誣衊因扔磚而畏罪自殺。","createTime":"2019-07-25T05:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:04:03.000Z","uid":10014,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6aacf6889081eb810d682f68cfd23a4feeed5e3c","tid":1363050,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"親屬既聲明：<br />\n<br />\n聲明<br />\n<br />\n本人係22號沙田廣源村死者嘅親戚，由於近日網上出現咗不實消息，希望借呢個平台可以幫死者澄清一下。<br />\n<br />\n死者政治立場明確，的確曾經有參加遊行活動，但亦係和平地散去。今次發生不幸事件，主要因為家庭問題而發生悲劇，並唔係網上所講嘅因為政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n近幾日在「泛民可恥行為事件簿」中所載, 稱死者有參與非法集結同掟磚頭，所以畏罪自殺。在此澄清一下死者並非因為呢件事而自殺。另外，之前網上流傳三張全身相，絕非死者本人。<br />\n<br />\n在此真心希望大家可以尊重死者，死者家屬唔希望死者嘅離開與任何政治因素牽涉，只想死者可以安息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫手到以下post進行report，謝謝！</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/434483659936746/posts/2565703660148058?s=100008433280022&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F434483659936746%2Fposts%2F2565703660148058%3Fs%3D100008433280022%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=ac36d0f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/434483659936746/posts/2565703660148058?s=100008433280022&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9tv3Xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9tv3Xu.png&h=a46411f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0052c9e3d5d2dc4b950d1fb730b67c81357d0148","tid":1363050,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52db282fc126d9d8f3d2a9efaf1459d2fcd16c06","tid":1363050,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj